| Route | Page | Access Role | Key Components |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/login` | Login page | Public | shadcn Card + Form |
| `/dashboard` | Admin KPI Overview | Admin | Recharts bar/pie charts |
| `/agents` | Agent List + Hierarchy Tree | Admin | DataTable, TreeView |
| `/agents/[id]` | Agent Profile + Ledger | Admin | Tabs, Commission table |
| `/agents/new` | Create/Edit Agent | Admin | Form with parent selector |
| `/leads` | Lead Table with filters | Admin, Salesperson | DataTable, Status badges |
| `/leads/[id]` | Lead Detail + Pipeline | Admin, Salesperson | Timeline, Status stepper |
| `/leads/new` | Submit Lead (dup check) | All roles | Multi-phone form, real-time check |
| `/deals` | All Deals Table | Admin | DataTable, Value summary |
| `/deals/[id]` | Deal Detail + Commissions | Admin | "Mark Paid" button triggers engine |
| `/commissions` | Commission Ledger | Admin | Filterable table, approve/dispute |
| `/payouts` | Finance Payout Queue | Admin | Pending payouts, record payment |
| `/my` | Agent Self-Service | Agent | Personal leads, earnings, statement |

