## Implementation Phases (Expanded)

### Phase 1: Foundation
- Initialize Next.js with `--typescript --tailwind --app`
- Install & configure Prisma with SQLite
- Install shadcn/ui (init + all needed components)
- Install Recharts, React Hook Form, Zod, Zustand, NextAuth, bcryptjs

### Phase 2: Auth & Roles
- NextAuth credentials provider (email + hashed password)
- Route-protecting middleware (`ADMIN`, `SALESPERSON`, `AGENT`)
- Login page with shadcn Card + Form

### Phase 3: Layout Shell
- App shell with sidebar navigation (shadcn Sheet + NavigationMenu)
- Dark mode toggle (shadcn ThemeProvider)
- Role-aware nav items (Agents see only `/my`, Admins see everything)

### Phase 4: Agent Module
- Agent CRUD with hierarchy (parent selector dropdown)
- Agent hierarchy visualization (tree or org chart)
- Agent detail page with commission history

### Phase 5: Lead Module
- Lead submission with real-time duplicate phone detection
- Multi-phone contact form (React Hook Form `useFieldArray`)
- Lead pipeline (table with status column + quick-update dropdown)
- Lead detail with activity timeline (🆕 uses LeadActivity model)
- Lead assignment to salesperson

### Phase 6: Deal & Commission Engine
- Deal creation linked to WON leads
- "Mark Payment Received" → triggers `calculateCommissions()` graph traversal
- Commission ledger with Approve / Dispute / Pay actions
- Payout recording with method and reference fields (🆕)

### Phase 7: Dashboards & Analytics (🆕 — not in original)
- **Admin Dashboard:** Total revenue, total commission liability, deals by status (Recharts BarChart, PieChart)
- **Agent Leaderboard:** Top 10 by conversion rate (Recharts)
- **Agent Self-Service `/my`:** Personal leads, pending earnings, paid history
- **Monthly Statement:** Per-agent summary (future: PDF via `@react-pdf/renderer`)

---

## Business Rules Enforced in Code

| # | Rule | Enforcement |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | **Phone uniqueness** | `@unique` constraint + API pre-check |
| 2 | **Owner immutability** | Server action NEVER updates `ownerId` |
| 3 | **Commission trigger** | Only fires on `paymentReceived: false → true` |
| 4 | **Rate lock** | 🆕 Rate read from Agent at deal-close → stored in `Commission.rate` |
| 5 | **No orphan leads** | FK constraint on `ownerId` |
| 6 | **No agent lead without ID** | Agent must have `agentCode` before submitting |
| 7 | **Cycle-safe hierarchy** | `visited` Set in graph traversal |
| 8 | **First-entry-wins** | Timestamp-based: first agent to register a phone number owns it |
| 9 | **Finance approval gate** | 🆕 Commission goes PENDING → APPROVED → PAID (manual approval step) |

