## What I Added vs. Original Plan

| Area | Original Plan | 🆕 My Addition |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | ❌ Not planned | ✅ NextAuth with 3 roles + middleware |
| Agent Code | ❌ Missing | ✅ `agentCode` unique identifier (AGT-0042) |
| Commission Rate Lock | ❌ Not considered | ✅ Rate stored at deal-close time in `Commission.rate` |
| CLOSER role | ❌ Only OWNER + REFERRER | ✅ Separate CLOSER commission for executing salesperson |
| OVERRIDE role | ❌ Not modeled | ✅ Commission for every parent in the agent tree |
| Payout model | ❌ Missing | ✅ Full `Payout` table with bank method + UTR |
| Audit trail | ❌ Missing | ✅ `LeadActivity` log (who changed what, when) |
| Analytics | ❌ Not planned | ✅ Recharts dashboards for Admin + Agent |
| Agent self-service | ❌ Not planned | ✅ `/my` page for agents to see their ledger |
| Phone label | ❌ Single type | ✅ Label field (Work / WhatsApp / Home) |
| DB Indexes | ✅ Mentioned SQL | ✅ Added 5 Prisma indexes for production performance |
| Soft delete | ❌ Not considered | ✅ `isActive` flag on Agent |
| Dispute flow | ❌ Not considered | ✅ DISPUTED status + `disputeNote` field |
| Finance approval | ❌ Auto-paid | ✅ PENDING → APPROVED → PAID workflow |
| Deal category | ❌ Not modeled | ✅ Category field for variable commission rates |
| Cycle detection | ✅ Mentioned | ✅ Fully implemented with `visited` Set |

